<HEADLINE>
FT  04 MAY 94 / Brussels to probe takeover
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The European Commission said yesterday it would examine the takeover of UK
reinsurance group NRG Victory Reinsurance by Employers Reassurance and
Denmark's Nordisk Reinsurance Company, which are units of General Electric
Company.
The Commission said a preliminary probe showed that the takeover could fall
under EU merger rules, but it reserved a final decision.
