 ----------------------------------------------------------
200 members elected proportionately from national election
lists, except in the case of the National party, which had
no national list and will choose all its representatives
from provincial lists
 ----------------------------------------------------------
200 members elected proportionately from provincial lists
 ----------------------------------------------------------
                     SENTATE OF 90 SEATS
 ----------------------------------------------------------
10 members nominated by each of the nine provincial
legislatures
