30 seats      North-West
30 seats      Northern Cape
42 seats      Western Cape
40 seats      Northern Transvaal
30 seats      Eastern Transvaal
81 seats      KwaZulu/Natal
56 seats      Eastern Cape
30 seats      Orange Free State
